---
// CareerTimeline.astro — Visual timeline for career/education journey
---

<section class="career-timeline">
  <h2 class="section-title">Career Journey</h2>
  <ol class="timeline-list">
    <li class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h3>Research Assistant</h3>
        <span class="timeline-org">Geoseismal Research Center</span>
        <span class="timeline-period">Feb 2026 – Present</span>
        <p>Conducting geophysics research with focus on seismic data analysis and interpretation.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h3>Geophysics Software Intern — Earthquake Early Warning Systems</h3>
        <span class="timeline-org">BMKG (Badan Meteorologi, Klimatologi, dan Geofisika)</span>
        <span class="timeline-period">Feb 2024 – Jun 2024</span>
        <ul>
          <li>Developed EEWS prototype for Central & East Java, integrating real-time processing and alert delivery.</li>
          <li>Engineered Python pipelines for 58-station seismic data analysis.</li>
          <li>Optimized P-wave detection and magnitude estimation (MAE ≈ 0.42).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h3>Laboratory Teaching Assistant — Computational Methods</h3>
        <span class="timeline-org">Universitas Gadjah Mada</span>
        <span class="timeline-period">Aug 2023 – Jan 2024</span>
        <ul>
          <li>Mentored 50+ students in Python for scientific computing.</li>
          <li>Developed hands-on practicum and evaluated student work.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h3>Bachelor of Science in Geophysics</h3>
        <span class="timeline-org">Universitas Gadjah Mada</span>
        <span class="timeline-period">2019 – 2026</span>
        <p>Graduated with GPA 3.35. Thesis: ML-based earthquake parameter estimation for early warning systems.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>

<style>
.career-timeline {
  padding: 3rem 1rem;
  background: var(--color-bg, #f8fafc);
}
.section-title {
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.timeline-list {
  position: relative;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 0 0 2rem;
  max-width: 700px;
  border-left: 3px solid #c7d2fe;
  list-style: none;
}
.timeline-item {
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.timeline-marker {
  position: absolute;
  left: -1.25rem;
  top: 0.5rem;
  width: 1.25rem;
  height: 1.25rem;
  background: #6366f1;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 3px solid #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px #c7d2fe;
}
.timeline-content {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  margin-left: 0.5rem;
}
.timeline-org {
  display: block;
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #6366f1;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.timeline-period {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: #64748b;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .timeline-list {
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }
  .timeline-content {
    padding: 1rem;
  }
}
</style>
